"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/746514","Department for Culture, Media and Sport","false","2017-06-29","<p>We are committed to supporting and promoting a thriving live music industry. We support small music venues through business rates relief, by looking at the agent of change principle and with simplified licensing and planning rules.</p><p> </p>","West Suffolk","Matt Hancock",,"2017-06-29T16:57:53.897Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/746514/answer","Biography information for Matt Hancock","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/746514/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/746514/answer",,,,,"10","Culture, Media and Sport","Culture, Media and Sport","2017-06-26","Music: Small Businesses","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Culture, Media and Sport, what plans she has to improve financial and statutory support for small music venues.","false","Biography information for Jo Stevens","Cardiff Central","Jo Stevens","900091"
